            <title>[CXF-3142] BusFactory holds static reference to defaultBus</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3142</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;BusFactory.defaultBus is a static strong reference. I think I&apos;ve proved that this is why CXF builds like to run out of memory.&lt;/p&gt;

